Indeed!



16
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:26,040
Ito's rapid improvement has given women's judo a shot in the arm!

17
00:02:26,040 --> 00:02:27,200
Don't be so optimistic!

18
00:02:27,750 --> 00:02:32,380
