21
00:02:41,900 --> 00:02:43,640
And be a lot tougher on her this time!

22
00:02:43,970 --> 00:02:49,620
Yes, sir! Ito will perform brilliantly at the All-Japan Championships!

23
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:52,650
She will then go to the Barcelona Olympics with Yawara-san!






24
00:02:52,650 --> 00:02:56,220
Mm-hmm! And those two'll snatch them gold medals!

25
00:02:56,220 --> 00:02:58,650
Yutenji, wanna go out for some udon?


26
