29
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,200
That's strange.

30
00:03:33,200 --> 00:03:37,270
They told me she was home with a cold when I called Saikai U.

31
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:42,280
Maybe I should get some tea and wait by the station.

32
00:03:55,210 --> 00:03:56,250
Fujiko-san!

33
00:03:56,790 --> 00:03:57,960
Inokuma-san!

34
00:03:57,960 --> 00:04:01,960
You shouldn't be here if you have a cold.

35
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:03,200
I don't have a cold.

36
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:05,470
Oh? Then why did you miss practice?

37
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:12,980
Inokuma-san, I might not be able to enter the All-Japan Tournament.

38
00:04:13,350 --> 00:04:14,380
Huh?

39
00:04:14,380 --> 00:04:16,670
Why? Are you injured?





40
00:04:20,030 --> 00:04:24,020
I see. You must not like judo anymore.

41
00:04:24,020 --> 00:04:28,530
I understand. How can a girl like a sweaty combat sport anyway?

42
00:04:28,530 --> 00:04:32,000
Th-That's not it! I love judo!

43
00:04:32,000 --> 00:04:33,980
Then why?

44
00:04:33,980 --> 00:04:39,410
You were so into it! And you're at the top of your game right now.

45
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:52,180
Fujiko-san, if something is bothering you, tell me!

46
00:04:52,180 --> 00:04:55,390
I'll do anything I can to help!

47
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:59,010
Fujiko-san.

48
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,090
Inokuma-san...

49
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:13,950
I'm late.

50
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:15,650
For what?

51
00:05:16,210 --> 00:05:17,290
You know.

52
00:05:19,130 --> 00:05:20,000
Sorry, what?

53
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:25,470
I'm... "late" late.

54
00:05:29,090 --> 00:05:32,970
Wait. You mean... you're...

55
00:05:44,740 --> 00:05:46,900
What am I going to do?

56
00:05:49,950 --> 00:05:52,450
Sign: Takemura Obstetrics and Gynecology#

57
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,720
Thank you very much.

58
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:09,750
Fujiko-san.

59
00:06:16,660 --> 00:06:20,320
Fujiko-san, what did they say?

60
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:21,690
Fujiko-san!

61
00:06:25,110 --> 00:06:28,200
Fujiko-san, what did your doctor say?

62
00:06:39,670 --> 00:06:41,040
He said October 10th!

63
00:06:42,740 --> 00:06:44,460
That's when it's due!


64
00:06:49,840 --> 00:06:51,970
All right, I'm going to do it!

65
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:57,060
I'm going to give birth to a kid as full of life as Inokuma-san!

66
00:06:57,060 --> 00:06:58,180
Fujiko-san!


67
00:06:58,770 --> 00:07:03,210
I made up my mind when the doctor congratulated me!

68
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:07,190
Mothers are always strong!


69
00:07:08,530 --> 00:07:10,200
Fujiko-san...

70
00:07:12,950 --> 00:07:14,930
Congratulations, Fujiko-san!

71
00:07:23,710 --> 00:07:26,090
The All-Japan Tournament is almost here.

72
00:07:28,550 --> 00:07:33,470
We'll probably see you and Inokuma-san in the finals, like last year.

73
00:07:33,470 --> 00:07:37,290
This time I'll be there to cheer you on.

74
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:42,480
Still, I'm not going to just sit back and cheer.

75
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:46,690
I'll also be working full throttle toward the Barcelona Olympics.

76
00:07:47,820 --> 00:07:50,110
Hanazono-san... do you like children?

77
00:07:51,570 --> 00:07:53,240
Of course!

78
00:07:53,240 --> 00:07:56,490
The kids who live around my judo dorm have become attached to me.

79
00:07:56,490 --> 00:08:00,830
Every day, I throw them and knock them down, and we all have fun!





80
00:08:01,410 --> 00:08:03,420
You have big hands.

81
00:08:03,420 --> 00:08:07,380
Putting babies into baths is a job reserved for daddies with big hands.

82
00:08:09,130 --> 00:08:14,050
I could put quintuplets or sextuplets in the bath with my hands!

83
00:08:14,050 --> 00:08:15,890
Good luck, Papa.

84
00:08:16,390 --> 00:08:17,850
Papa, huh?

85
00:08:17,850 --> 00:08:22,810
If we do have a baby, we'll make it practice judo by the time it walks,

86
00:08:22,810 --> 00:08:25,230
and it will become a world champion like Inokuma... or not.





87
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:27,940
I thought about that as well!

88
00:08:27,940 --> 00:08:30,280
It looks like great minds think alike!

89
00:08:30,840 --> 00:08:34,110
I can't wait for Health and Sports Day on October 10th.

90
00:08:34,110 --> 00:08:35,110
Can't wait for what?

91
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:38,660
There's... a baby on the way.

92
00:08:38,660 --> 00:08:41,540
Well, that's great! Whose baby?

93
00:08:41,540 --> 00:08:43,500
Yours and mine.

94
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:45,420
Oh, is that true?

95
00:08:56,340 --> 00:09:00,010
Wh-What did you just say?

96
00:09:00,010 --> 00:09:03,310
I apologize sincerely for causing this inconvenience.

97
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:07,810
I need to take a maternity leave due to pregnancy.

98
00:09:09,820 --> 00:09:11,320
Sign: Inokuma#

99
00:09:13,260 --> 00:09:14,770
Hanazono-kun?

100
00:09:15,820 --> 00:09:20,330
Inokuma, don't say anything.
 Be my randori practice partner.

101
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:31,210
Not enough! Throw me down harder!


102
00:09:33,090 --> 00:09:37,680
Don't hold back! Throw me down like you mean it!

103
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:41,600
What have you done?!

104
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:46,600
October 10th?! What about the All-Japan Judo Championships?!

105
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:51,270
You're the hope of Saikai U...
 no, of Japanese women's judo!

106
00:09:51,770 --> 00:09:54,070
I'm truly sorry for what I've done.


107
00:09:54,740 --> 00:10:00,070
You two are my masters and made me into the judo player I am today,

108
00:10:00,070 --> 00:10:02,740
yet I spat on that generosity.

109
00:10:03,830 --> 00:10:05,660
But I...

110
00:10:06,500 --> 00:10:09,040
Master! Say something to her!

111
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:20,550
You blithering idiot.


112
00:10:28,860 --> 00:10:33,850
M-More! Throw me down more till I can't see straight!

113
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,870
I... I...

114
00:10:42,450 --> 00:10:43,990
Hanazono-kun?

115
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:47,790
Forgive me, Inokuma!

116
00:10:47,790 --> 00:10:50,750
I'm... I'm such a...

117
00:10:53,590 --> 00:10:56,340
Why do you feel you have to apologize?

118
00:11:01,390 --> 00:11:03,640
Congratulations, Hanazono-kun.

119
00:11:04,100 --> 00:11:05,650
Inokuma...

120
00:11:18,860 --> 00:11:21,450
Sign: Ito Gardens
 Fine Tea#

121
00:11:21,450 --> 00:11:22,360
Wha...

122
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:23,370
Huh...

123
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:26,870
What did you say? S-Say that one more time!

124
00:11:26,870 --> 00:11:30,500
Well, we're... having a baby.

125
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:33,880
I'm sorry! I take full responsibility!

126
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:36,420
I-I...

127
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:37,920
I'll kill you!

128
00:11:37,920 --> 00:11:38,840
Dad!

129
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:41,380
I-I plan to take full responsibility!

130
00:11:41,380 --> 00:11:44,470
Responsibility? Who do you think you are?

131
00:11:44,470 --> 00:11:48,180
You violated our only daughter, and this is how you act?!

132
00:11:48,180 --> 00:11:49,890
Dad, stop!

133
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:55,400
We shouldn't have sent her to Tokyo alone!


134
00:11:55,840 --> 00:11:59,230
We shouldn't have let her play judo!

135
00:11:59,230 --> 00:12:02,500
Judo has nothing to do with this, Mom!

136
00:12:02,500 --> 00:12:04,640
No, she's completely right!

137
00:12:04,640 --> 00:12:09,360
If it weren't for judo, you wouldn't have come in contact with this animal!

138
00:12:09,360 --> 00:12:11,350
Dad, stop!

139
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:14,390
Fujiko's life is ruined!

140
00:12:15,380 --> 00:12:16,380
I'll kill you!

141
00:12:16,380 --> 00:12:21,060
Father! I, Hanazono Kaoru, will take care of everything. Believe me!

142
00:12:21,060 --> 00:12:24,000
Nobody said you can call me "Father"!

143
00:12:25,760 --> 00:12:26,910
Fujiko!



144
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:32,730
Fujiko's... Fujiko's having morning sickness!

145
00:12:32,730 --> 00:12:34,660
You bastard, I'll kill you!

146
00:12:34,660 --> 00:12:38,770
I-I, Hanazono, will give Fujiko-san a happy life!

147
00:12:38,770 --> 00:12:42,690
What? After you've brought such misery to this family?!

148
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:48,620
Ito Fujiko's not at practice.

149
00:12:48,620 --> 00:12:52,250
And with Inagaki off at training camp, there's no news to be had at Saikai U.

150
00:12:52,880 --> 00:12:56,350
Hell, this season we sports writers have nothing to write about anyway.

151
00:12:59,860 --> 00:13:01,760
Swear you won't tell anyone!

152
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,630
Come on, what is it?

153
00:13:03,630 --> 00:13:06,220
I know the real reason why Ito-san hasn't been coming to practice!

154
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:08,180
She's not out with a cold?

155
00:13:08,550 --> 00:13:10,940
It's not a cold!

156
00:13:10,940 --> 00:13:13,180
I heard she's pregnant!

157
00:13:13,520 --> 00:13:15,270
P-Pregnant?!

158
00:13:15,270 --> 00:13:17,220
Hush, you're too loud!

159
00:13:17,220 --> 00:13:20,360
No way. I don't believe it! This is <i>the</i> Ito-san, right?

160
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:26,420
It's true. I heard Coaches Yutenji and Nakamura talking about it!

161
00:13:26,420 --> 00:13:27,320
No way!

162
00:13:27,910 --> 00:13:29,990
Man, that Fujiko-san.






163
00:13:30,620 --> 00:13:34,640
How could she get a cold with the All-Japans coming up?

164
00:13:34,640 --> 00:13:35,960
Maybe I should see how she's holding up.

165
00:13:41,760 --> 00:13:43,670
Isn't that the writer from <i>Sports Tokyo</i> ?

166
00:13:43,670 --> 00:13:45,380
We reporters have it tough.

167
00:13:46,130 --> 00:13:49,050
Hello? Can we change the front page headlines?

168
00:13:49,050 --> 00:13:51,810
I got a scoop! A huge one!


169
00:13:51,810 --> 00:13:55,100
The hope of Japanese women's judo, Ito Fujiko, is pregnant!

170
00:13:56,730 --> 00:13:59,520
Dammit! It's that bastard from <i>All Sports Daily</i> !

171
00:13:59,520 --> 00:14:01,200
Anyway, I'm on my way back!

172
00:14:01,770 --> 00:14:03,760
Hey, come back here!

173
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:04,690
What did you say?!

174
00:14:07,350 --> 00:14:07,900
Wait!

175
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,750
Watch where you're going, dumbass!


176
00:14:15,580 --> 00:14:18,150
Pregnant? Fujiko-san?

177
00:14:20,330 --> 00:14:20,580
What now, media jackal? I ain't got nothing to say to you!

178
00:14:20,580 --> 00:14:24,210
Sign: Inokuma#
What now, media jackal? I ain't got nothing to say to you!

179
00:14:24,210 --> 00:14:27,420
You may not wanna talk, but I do!

180
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:28,720
Get Yawara-san out here!

181
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:31,180
Yawara's prohibited from seeing men!

182
00:14:31,180 --> 00:14:34,640
She's on complete lockdown until the Olympics.

183
00:14:34,640 --> 00:14:35,470
Now get lost!

184
00:14:35,890 --> 00:14:37,940
That's not why I'm here!

185
00:14:37,940 --> 00:14:40,730
This is important! Call Yawara-san—

186
00:14:40,730 --> 00:14:43,070
Grandpa, what do you want for lunch?

187
00:14:43,070 --> 00:14:43,980
Matsuda-san!

188
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:46,990
Yawara-san, is it true that Fujiko-san is pregnant?

189
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:53,080
I have no idea what you're talking about.

190
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:55,820
You media jackals have sharp noses!

191
00:14:55,820 --> 00:14:56,750
Grandpa!

192
00:14:58,620 --> 00:15:00,140
So it's true!

193
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:00,920
No, um...

194
00:15:00,920 --> 00:15:02,250
It's about to blow up.

195
00:15:02,880 --> 00:15:05,250
It'll be revealed in tomorrow's <i>Sports Tokyo</i> !

196
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:13,760
Headline: Women's Judo Rocked!!
Sidebar: Women's Judo's Hope, Ito Fujiko Pregnant!! Will She Retire?!#

197
00:15:13,760 --> 00:15:16,720
Inokuma-san! Excuse me, can we have a word?

198
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:19,180
Is Ito Fujiko-san in there?

199
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:21,730
You can send out Yawara-san! Please give us a comment!

200
00:15:21,730 --> 00:15:24,730
What's the racket so danged early?!

201
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:26,620
Gah, it's her grandpa!

202
00:15:26,620 --> 00:15:30,320
It's an honor to see you. May we have a word?



203
00:15:30,320 --> 00:15:33,360
Oh, you wanna hear the heroic saga of my youth?

204
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:36,600
It was back during the February 26th Incident of '36.



205
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:39,540
Dark clouds were looming all over the globe at the time...

206
00:15:39,540 --> 00:15:43,920
E-Excuse me, but we've heard that story three times already.

207
00:15:43,920 --> 00:15:46,600
Good, then I'll switch over to my roaring post-war years then!

208
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,960
We're not here for that!

209
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:53,220
We're here about Ito Fujiko's pregnancy that <i>Sports Tokyo</i> scooped us on!

210
00:15:53,220 --> 00:15:54,850
What do you say about that article?

211
00:15:54,850 --> 00:15:57,310
Is it true? Who's the father?

212
00:15:57,310 --> 00:16:00,330
How do you feel about your prized pupil becoming pregnant?





213
00:16:02,690 --> 00:16:04,690
She's pregnant, so what's done is done.

214
00:16:04,690 --> 00:16:09,340
But she's our hope for the Barcelona Olympics. You trained her yourself!

215
00:16:09,340 --> 00:16:11,700
You're down one Olympic medal hopeful!

216
00:16:11,700 --> 00:16:16,580
Grow the hell up, and quit making such a damn fuss over this!

217
00:16:16,580 --> 00:16:20,540
My Yawara will win the medals Beanpole should've!

218
00:16:21,580 --> 00:16:23,780
Wait a second! Inokuma-san!

219
00:16:23,780 --> 00:16:27,780
Are you hiding Ito Fujiko in your residence?!

220
00:16:27,780 --> 00:16:29,550
Send her out if she's in there!

221
00:16:30,180 --> 00:16:32,050
Sheesh, she'd better thank me.

222
00:16:40,140 --> 00:16:42,770
What will you do from here on out?

223
00:16:43,350 --> 00:16:47,400
I intend to marry her and work for our child.

224
00:16:47,900 --> 00:16:49,400
I see.

225
00:16:49,400 --> 00:16:52,400
Good luck! Show 'em what a man can do.

226
00:16:52,400 --> 00:16:53,810
I will.

227
00:16:56,880 --> 00:16:59,030
Don't worry about Fujiko-san.

228
00:16:59,030 --> 00:17:01,160
She's hiding out at Yawara-san's place.






229
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:04,330
Jigoro-san and Yawara-san will figure something out.

230
00:17:07,250 --> 00:17:12,210
The media must have Yawara-san's place completely surrounded by now.

231
00:17:15,130 --> 00:17:16,730
I'm going to be a man!

232
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:22,350
I'm responsible for all of this! I can't make any more trouble for others.

233
00:17:22,970 --> 00:17:25,850
Also, I'll be the one to protect Fujiko-san!

234
00:17:26,920 --> 00:17:28,810
Hey, Hanazono!


235
00:17:29,060 --> 00:17:30,860
There you have it.

236
00:17:30,860 --> 00:17:33,540
Ito Fujiko-san has not returned to her apartment,

237
00:17:33,540 --> 00:17:35,920
and we have yet to locate her.

238
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:41,830
Rumor has it that she's hiding out here at the residence of Inokuma Jigoro, her instructor.

239
00:17:41,830 --> 00:17:44,320
Because she's an Olympic gold medal hopeful,

240
00:17:44,320 --> 00:17:49,290
we highly anticipate her next move in this developing scandal.

241
00:17:49,290 --> 00:17:49,980
Sign: Look Today#

242
00:17:49,980 --> 00:17:52,760
That's the report from Uchida at the scene.
Sign: Look Today#

243
00:17:52,760 --> 00:17:53,800
We're certainly curious as to where the person of interest, Ito Fujiko-san, is hiding out.
