244
00:17:53,800 --> 00:17:56,880
We're certainly curious as to where the person of interest, Ito Fujiko-san, is hiding out.

245
00:17:56,880 --> 00:17:58,800
Yes, indeed.

246
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:00,800
It's like I'm a criminal.

247
00:18:01,350 --> 00:18:05,810
Fujiko-san, you shouldn't be watching the TV. It's not good for the baby.

248
00:18:05,810 --> 00:18:09,040
...she might return to that scene, so we'll wait an entire night if we—

249
